highlights.text: “24 Songs” by void, ciaffa, and fedo DJ is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Netherlands, up 13 spots at #77.
“Baila de Gasolina” by Effe Serieus has been on Viral Songs Netherlands the longest, at 207 days straight.
Bente has the most spots on Viral Songs Netherlands. “Kan Je Me Zien” is the highest at #4.
“Octopus (100.000 Hände)” by Mountain Crew is the highest new entry on Viral Songs Netherlands at #1.
